Jesse Jutkowitz v. Department of Health Services et al. (12244)

Foti, Heiman and Schaller, Js.

Argued February 14 decision released March 14, 1995 Henry A. Saltón, assistant attorney general, with whom, on the brief, were Richard Blumenthal, attorney general, and Richard J. Lynch, assistant attorney general, for the appellants-appellees (defendants). *905Hanon W. Russell, for the appellee-appellant (plaintiff). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
